 \frac{\partial \rho}{\partial t} + \frac{\partial}{\partial x}(\rho v)=0 
 \frac{\partial \rho}{\partial t} + v\frac{\partial \rho}{\partial x} = -\rho \frac{\partial v}{\partial x} 
