(a(t),b(t))
a'(t) = v(a(t),t)
b'(t) = v(b(t),t)
 \frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}t} \int_{a(t)}^{b(t)} \rho(x,t) \, \mathrm{d}x = 0. 
